metadata.name: Ape
metadata.description: In 2249, Dr. Serkhat conducts an important experiment on animals. To control them, he inserts chips into their brains, but the advanced Artificial Intelligence of that time hacks the chip system to control humanity and begins to live in the brains of cyber animals by replicating itself. The human race, defeated by the intelligence of animals, begins to live underground. A large part of the population is under control. Now the World is ruled by Cyber ​​Animals.
